snippet.title: Rocky Ruins - Official launch trailer
snippet.description:
Here is the launch trailer for my little game, which I made over a few weeks. It is now available on Itch.io and Kartridge to play i hope I get feedback on my game so far.

https://artificial-games.itch.io/rocky-ruins
